| SPL Rule: Account Enumeration / Discovery
| MITRE ATT&CK: T1087 - Account Discovery
| Severity: Medium
| Source: Real auth.log from Metasploitable2 VM (192.168.56.104)
| Result: admin, administrator, guest, oracle, test, user enumerated (5 attempts each)

index=lab sourcetype=linux_secure "Invalid user"
| rex "Invalid user (?<username>\w+) from"
| stats count by username
| sort -count
| eval alert="Account Enumeration Detected"
